name: Quantum Lighter
description:
The Quantum Lighter. It’s truly revolutionary. This lighter has been constructed from a unique polymer, rarely found in consumer products, that exists entirely in a state of quantum superposition.

It’s simply, incredible.

Not only can it produce, light, sound And heat from the use of it’s simple, yet elegant ferrocerium mechanism, the features made possible from it’s super positioned state are simply astounding. 

With the quantum lighter and its trademark super-positioned polymer, we’ve been able to make it both exist and not exist, at the same time. It’s truly the Schrödinger’s cat of the hand held flame producing device world.

What this means for you, is that in your hour of need, the Quantum Lighter is capable of fabricating itself in your previously empty pocket, as if by magic. We’ve even witnessed situations where Prang Out’s Quantum Lighter has re-emerged in the pockets of those close by to you. It’s truly remarkable.

Please note:
As this is not a Bic branded lighter, you are not susceptible to the curse of the white lighter, unless you are age 27 and a successful musician.
